data.text: @GreyFactionTST Those high notes are pretty suspect, if you ask me. (Honestly, i think the scariest thing is people believe this tripe. )

@GreyFactionTST I went to an old cemetery with a co worker and there was an old stage. We both walked up the stairs, standing on the platform and it creeped us both out. Took a bit to creep us out since him and I worked together at a different cemetery.

@GreyFactionTST What is described as rituals, sacrifices, and other behaviors doesn’t or hasn’t occurred (USA) in about a 75 years. I’ve seen the metal stages and structures that are now just sitting there for historical reasons.

@GreyFactionTST Having sat through "All I Want for Christmas is You" approximately 12,000 times on the radio during the holidays, I find the idea that Mariah Carey is aligned with some dark power to be perfectly viable.
